 The following is a bill which passed the House, providing for the protection of the frontier of the State of Texas.

It was advocated by the representatives of that State with a degree of earnestness which testified their devotion to the Commonwealth which honored them with her confidence.

It was introduced by Mr. Herbert, of that State;
